 (2,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Acapulco de Juárez has always been characterized by its strong tourist impact, both national and international; featured in hundreds of films, a favorite of well-known Hollywood stars from the 1950s and 1960s, attractive to hotel impresarios and investors, and today, the destination of many a Mexico City inhabitant seeking sun and sea on the weekends.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
