 (29,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">New York\''s capital city of Albany is more than just a collection of imposing, 1960s-style government buildings, it is also home to world-class museums, galleries, eateries and quaint neighborhoods with unique, 19th-century architecture.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
