 (59,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Amsterdam, the magnificent capital of The Netherlands is also its commercial center, and home to the world\''s oldest stock exchange. Recognized as a cityin the 14th Century, Amsterdam reaches its successful peak after blossoming into a vibrant merchant town that was part of the famed Hanseatic League. Today, this brilliant canal-lined city is one of the most visited places in the world. Divided into eight boroughs, each of Amsterdam\''s neighborhoods are full of a colorful, distinct character that is their very own.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
