 (97,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Prettier than most postcards, Antigua is a quintessential island paradise. It is split into six parishes, each of which hosts virtually every blue-green hue imaginable. Off the beach, visitors will find cultural sights like churches and museums mixed with inexhaustible natural attractions, among them karst formations and hike-able hills. Start in stunning capital St. John\''s and work your way down the list of Antigua\''s picturesque parishes!</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
