 (144,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Casino resorts and the Boardwalk are the main attractions here. The boardwalks of Atlantic City and Ventnor combine to make one of the longest boardwalks in the world. This is the place to entertain the whole family, indoor and outdoor, early morning till late night.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
