 (280,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Nestled in the verdant mountainous surroundings of Basque Country, Bilbao is northern Spain\''s rich cultural hotspot that basks in the glory of its prolific modern architecture it is known for. An industrial port city, the city of Bilbao is divided into districts, but we get a better picture of the true topography if we keep in mind that the city is divided by Nervión estuary into two halves.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
