 (422,'Facade of a fort in Kolkata.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
 (423,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">With a vast history behind it, Kolkata has gone through more than a few changes over the years. The neighborhoods of Kolkata are closely knit, often leaving one confused about the actual boundaries of certain areas. Moreover, the increasing population has led to expansion efforts in all directions from what used to be the initial city. The landscape of the city tends to change drastically from one area to the other, the only constants being the crowds and the traffic.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
 (424,'Facade of a fort in Kolkata.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
