 (701,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">The city of Edinburgh is basically split into two main districts — the Old Town and the New Town — with Princes Street Gardens separating the two. The surrounding areas offer a wealth of places to visit.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
