 (785,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">A spirited city filled to the brim with icons of culture, music and heritage, Galway enraptures visitors in with a vibe that is both inescapable and unforgettable. Ireland\''s sixth most populous city, Galway has many colorful and distinctive districts, despite its small size and population. This is partly due to the city\''s age and partly due to its dynamic growth. Like many older European cities, the periods of history which the city has witnessed have left their mark on the central and outlying areas.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
