 (803,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">A seaside city known for its prolific port activity throughout history, Genoa is the charming capital of the region of Liguria. It is split into nine administrative districts and boasts several notable neighborhoods therein. One of the larger cities in Italy, Genoa manages to pack in plenty of variety, offering visitors an experience that is at once elegant and casual, refined and down-home.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
