 (947,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">More than seven million people are crammed into the mere 1,100 square kilometers (425 square miles) that make up the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR). Not just a city of skyscrapers, there is also lush countryside, glorious national parks, and small rural communities to be found here.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
