 (956,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Honolulu is an ultra-modern city, the state capital of Hawaii and the gateway to the islands. The city is also Hawaii\''s largest and a bustling center of trade and commerce. Honolulu is home to a diverse population, its varied populous lending the island of O\''ahu the nickname - \"The Gathering Place.\"</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
