 (1049,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Key West lies on a silvery ribbon of islands that trail off the southern shore of Florida. Thanks to the ever-present warm weather and glistening seas, the islands have long been an escapist\''s nirvana. Eclectic and eccentric, wild and warm, blessed with some of Florida\''s most colorful characters and equally endowed with some of its most spectacular seascapes, the Keys are a wondrous paradise.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
