 (1088,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">One of Poland\''s oldest cities, Kraków\''s marvelous architecture and timeless heritage is the stuff of legends. Apart from being a prime commercial hotspot, life in Kraków also revolves around a series of artistic pursuits, highlighting its inextricable link to Polish legacy and culture. Kraków is a relatively small city and therefore easily discovered, allowing minimal use of maps and public transit. There are four main areas of interest to the first-time visitor.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
