 (1186,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Nestled in the river valleys of Chillon, Rimac and Lurin, Peru\''s capital city features a fascinating mix of colonial-era vestiges and burgeoning modernity. Lima, surrounded by a desert, consists of main districts in its neighborhood sprawl, that are further made up of smaller neighborhoods, or <em>barrios. </em>From the never-fading vibrancy of the Miraflores district, to the quaint atmosphere of the Centro Historico, each of Lima\''s neighborhoods offer a rich blend of history and culture to the modern traveler.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
