 (1195,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">The breathtaking City of Seven Hills is a maze of narrow streets laid centuries ago that together comprise one of the most cosmopolitan cities in Europe. The westernmost European capital, Lisbon is prized for its seamless mixture of tradition and modernity, not only offering great contrast but also striking a palpable balance. From vibrant and historic Alfama to young and lively Bairro Alto, the city has so much local flavor to offer through its sights, sounds, and many inviting neighborhoods.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
