 (1245,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">France\''s third largest city that is bisected by the Rhône and Saône rivers, Lyon is one of the nation\''s most culturally vibrant cities. With a robust appetite for gastronomy and with a rich historical heritage that is represented in its numerous architectural landmarks, Lyon is an underrated French haven. It has nine <em>arrondissements </em>or districts, four of which are classified as World Heritage Sites by UNESCO.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
