 (1264,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">One of Morocco\''s famed imperial cities that is also its capital, Marrakech is thick with centuries-old culture and heritage that percolates into inescapable nooks and corners of its stunning architecture and vestiges of history. This historic city, at the heart of which lies the storied Medina, is composed of a multitude of quarters or neighborhoods, each of which tells a riveting story about its magnificent past.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
