 (1274,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Melbourne is mixed bag when it comes to neighborhoods, which range from chic and trendy to bohemian and beachy. Each district has its own character, and the city at large takes cues from the rich and varied customs, beliefs, cuisines, and aesthetics of its delightfully multicultural population.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
