 (1369,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Moscow, the largest city in the European continent, is also the commercial, political and cultural epicenter of Russia. Set on the Moskva River, this colossal city, also known as The Third Rome, is dissected into twelve administrative <em>okrugs</em> and 123 districts. Some of its most prominent areas and neighborhoods have been highlighted below.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
