 (1558,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Enjoying more hours of sunshine than any other Australian capital, Perth is the place to take advantage of clean air, great beaches, and a laid-back lifestyle. The city is located on the Swan River, its suburbs sprawling out in a north-south direction and running east to the Darling Ranges. Locals refer to locations as being either north or south of the river, or in the hills.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
