 (1692,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">A city with a larger-than-life spirit, Reykjavik is Iceland\''s dynamic capital. This northern city is invigorating, a hotbed of innovation, design, gastronomy, culture and eye-popping natural beauty. A city that defies expectation and refuses to be labeled, Reykjavik is the very embodiment of the saying \"good things come in small packages.\''though small, the city has a number of distinct neighborhoods within its confines and is part of the larger Capital Region that engulfs five surrounding municipalities.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
