 (1975,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Ask a Stockholmer where they are from and they will most likely say the name of their closest subway station. As the lovely city sits on water, it is best to get around its narrow streets and alleys on public transport. Furthermore, the subway stations conveniently separate the different sections of the city.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
