 (2082,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Vancouver is a city that has it all; Set between the Pacific Ocean and the coastal mountains, Vancouver is blessed with both natural beauty and cosmopolitan flair. Gardens, parks, and beaches are as common here as heritage buildings, restaurants, and theaters. While maintaining the laid-back attitude of North America\''s West Coast, Vancouver has garnered an international spirit. As the third largest city in Canada, it boasts an unrivaled ethnic diversity and multicultural flavor. It\''s young, lively, and the jumping-off point for many spectacular outdoor activities.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
