 (2160,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">With its impressive monuments, famous museums, and stately government buildings, Washington DC is easily recognizable as the United States\'' capital city. The city\''s varied attractions bring millions of tourists each year. In fact, it is the second most visited city in the United States, after New York, and is among the top travel destinations in the world.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
