 (2421,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Thanks to its historical significance, spectacular baroque landmarks and growing popularity as a major science and research center, modern Heidelberg welcomes millions of guests on its riverside shores every year. Stretched across an area of 109 square kilometers (42 square miles) that are slotted into 14 major districts, this heavenly city, named a UNESCO City of Literature, is all set to win the hearts of tourists.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
