 (2523,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">What is old can still be new, and this is true of Newport today just as it was when the first settlers arrived in the harbor; a popular place of trade. Newport\''s rich cultural diversity comes from these early days of trade with the West Indies with settlers bringing once unusual items like pineapples with them. These became a welcome symbol displayed then and now in the districts of many Newport inns, restaurants, homes and shops. Whether you are visiting Newport for a mansion tour, a music festival, a yachting event or relaxing vacation on the beach, you will want to take your time exploring this old city by the sea.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
