 (2637,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Williamsburg, which played a crucial role in the American Revolution, is steeped in a rich history that is brought alive in its historic heart known as Colonial Williamsburg. The city is part of the the \"historic triangle\", which includes the colonial communities of Jamestown and Yorktown. The three settlements come together to form a heritage region that contains treasures found nowhere else in the country. Although Williamsburg loves recounting its storied past, it is also a modern city, making it one of the \''top 15 Cities in the United States\'', as announced by Travel + Leisure magazine\''s <em>2017 World\''s Best Awards.</em>  Made up of the old and the new, the city of Williamsburg is divided into four main parts: its historic heart known as Colonial Williamsburg, New Town, the College of William and Mary and surrounding attractions.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
