 (2951,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">Whenever Canada is mentioned, one of the first places that springs to mind is Banff. The Banff townsite sits within Banff National Park, Canada\''s oldest and most spectacular heritage site, surrounded by soaring peaks, dense coniferous forests and abundant wildlife. Home to many of the nation\''s most famous landmarks, and full of opportunities for adventure, Banff is Canada\''s ambassador to the world and one of the country\''s most-visited tourist attractions.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
