 (3056,'<div class=\"OverviewText\">This well-heeled ski resort is one of the Colorado\''s most expensive, packed with luxury hotels, fine dining restaurants and some of the Rockies most thrilling ski runs. Vail is a wintry haven that is a pleasure to visit in summer as well, its rivers and slopes teeming with opportunity for adventure. Vail, and its surroundings attract avid ski enthusiasts and outdoor adventurers, with a diverse offer that extends well beyond the snow-clad slopes into the culinary and cultural realms. There are museums to explore, festivals to attend and live entertainment to marvel at, as well as fabulous restaurants for a taste of foodie nirvana. While Vail Village itself is a hotbed of activities and attractions, there\''s plenty to catch your fancy nearby as well.</div><br><div class=\"FodorsCopyright\">&copy; Cityseeker</div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
